msgid "Empty the ${item:ch1.bucket_full}?"
msgstr "${item:ch1.bucket_full} を空にする？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_Lakeside_North.item_bucket_already_full.choice.Empty the ${item:ch1.bucket_full}?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "する"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_Lakeside_North.item_bucket_already_full.choice.Empty the ${item:ch1.bucket_full}?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "しない"

msgid "Empty the ${item:ch1.bucket_full_holy}?"
msgstr "${item:ch1.bucket_full_holy} を空にする？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_Lakeside_North.item_bucket_already_full.choice.Empty the ${item:ch1.bucket_full_holy}?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "する"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_Lakeside_North.item_bucket_already_full.choice.Empty the ${item:ch1.bucket_full_holy}?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "しない"

msgid "Fill up the ${item:ch1.bucket}?"
msgstr "${item:ch1.bucket} を満たす？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_Lakeside_North.item_bucket_on_water.choice.Fill up the ${item:ch1.bucket}?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "満たす"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_Lakeside_North.item_bucket_on_water.choice.Fill up the ${item:ch1.bucket}?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "満たさない"

msgid "What to do?"
msgstr "どうしよう？"

msgid "Kill it here"
msgstr "ここで殺す"

msgid "Release it around this area"
msgstr "この辺りで放す"

msgid "Do nothing"
msgstr "何もしない"

msgid "The crow shows no interest in it."
msgstr "カラスは何の興味も示さない。"

msgid "Nobody seems to want you, little one."
msgstr "誰もあなたを求めてないみたい。"

msgid "It refuses to leave the terrarium."
msgstr "イモムシは飼育箱から出たがらない。"

msgid "He must not like lavender very much..."
msgstr "ラベンダーはあまり好きじゃないんだね……"

msgid "(Looks like it couldn't swim after all.)"
msgstr "(やはり泳げなかったようだ。)"

msgid "(You can't place an incomplete doorknob...)"
msgstr "(未完成のドアノブを挿すことはできない……)"

msgid "Lavender flowers are growing all over this place."
msgstr "一面にラベンダーが咲いている。"

msgid "Pretty..."
msgstr "きれい……"

msgid "Take ${item:ch1.forest_lavender}?"
msgstr "${item:ch1.forest_lavender} を摘む？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_Lakeside_North.misc_lavender.choice.Take ${item:ch1.forest_lavender}?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "摘む"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_Lakeside_North.misc_lavender.choice.Take ${item:ch1.forest_lavender}?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "摘まない"

msgid "A crow standing on a log."
msgstr "丸太の上にカラスが止まっている。"

msgid "It's completely unfazed by the rain..."
msgstr "雨にも全然動じてない……"

msgid "A wooden log."
msgstr "丸太。"

msgid "I came from this direction. There's no reason to go back now."
msgstr "私はこっちから来た。今は戻る理由はない。"

msgid "You can't see the other side of the lake from here."
msgstr "ここからは湖の対岸は見えない。"

msgid "A small pond."
msgstr "小さな池。"

msgid "The caterpillar has moved on. You should too."
msgstr "イモムシは進んでいった。自分も進まないといけない。"

msgid "A door with two doorknobs."
msgstr "2つのドアノブがついたドア。"

msgid "Take a closer look?"
msgstr "詳しく見てみる？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_Lakeside_North.move_door.choice.Take a closer look?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "見てみる"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_Lakeside_North.move_door.choice.Take a closer look?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "やめておく"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_Lakeside_North.pnc_door_facility.dlg.lacie"
msgid "I placed my return doorknob. I shouldn't go anywhere else."
msgstr "もう帰還のドアノブを挿した。他の場所には行くべきじゃない。"

msgid "A stairway?"
msgstr "階段？"

msgid "It's so dark... I can't see anything..."
msgstr "真っ暗で……何も見えない……"

msgid "Agh... my head..."
msgstr "あぐ……頭が……"

msgid "What's going on...?"
msgstr "何が起きてるの……？"

msgid "This doorknob won't even turn."
msgstr "ドアノブは回りもしない。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_Lakeside_North.pnc_door_grave.dlg.lacie"
msgid "I placed my return doorknob. I shouldn't go anywhere else."
msgstr "もう帰還のドアノブを挿した。他の場所には行くべきじゃない。"

msgid "Hmm..."
msgstr "うーん……"

msgid "A strange door with two doorknobs... and empty slots to place more."
msgstr "不思議なドアにドアノブが2つと……追加で挿せる穴がいくつか。"

msgid "Amazing... my ${item:ch1.doorknob_return} fits right in. It wasn't a scam after all..."
msgstr "すごい……${item:ch1.doorknob_return}がぴったりはまる。偽物じゃなかったんだ……"

msgid "Still... I'm not ready to go home yet, but I'm glad to have found this door."
msgstr "とはいえ……まだ家に帰る時じゃないけど、でもこのドアが見つかってよかった。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_Lakeside_North.pnc_door_library.dlg.lacie"
msgid "I placed my return doorknob. I shouldn't go anywhere else."
msgstr "もう帰還のドアノブを挿した。他の場所には行くべきじゃない。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_Lakeside_North.pnc_door_moths.dlg.lacie"
msgid "I placed my return doorknob. I shouldn't go anywhere else."
msgstr "もう帰還のドアノブを挿した。他の場所には行くべきじゃない。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_Lakeside_North.pnc_door_shop.dlg.lacie"
msgid "I placed my return doorknob. I shouldn't go anywhere else."
msgstr "もう帰還のドアノブを挿した。他の場所には行くべきじゃない。"

msgid "An empty slot."
msgstr "何も挿さっていない穴。"

msgid "Place a doorknob?"
msgstr "ドアノブを挿す？"

msgid "Gray Doorknob"
msgstr "灰色のドアノブ"

msgid "Doorknob With Eye"
msgstr "目のドアノブ"

msgid "White Doorknob"
msgstr "白いドアノブ"

msgid "Doorknob With Flower"
msgstr "花のドアノブ"

msgid "Return Doorknob"
msgstr "帰還のドアノブ"

msgid "Do not"
msgstr "挿さない"

msgid "Is it really time to go home...?"
msgstr "本当に、ここで帰るべきなのかな……？"

msgid "Are you sure that you want to place this doorknob?"
msgstr "本当にこのドアノブを挿す？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_Lakeside_North.pnc_door_slot.choice.Are you sure that you want to place this doorknob?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "挿す"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_Lakeside_North.pnc_door_slot.choice.Are you sure that you want to place this doorknob?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "挿さない"
